Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.14,0:00:50.52,Caption,,0,0,0,,models, even right here, because right here, arena AI is saying that Kimi K3 is smarter
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.52,0:00:55.40,Caption,,0,0,0,,than fable five by not just like 1% but maybe I don't know, three to four, 5% and not
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.38,0:01:01.30,Caption,,0,0,0,,just which is a crazy thing to claim because fable five is supposed to be so strong.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,It's so smart and so capable, ultra on level AI that they can't even give it to the public.
